post.description:
Create a recording. ``recording_id`` omitted → server mints;
supplied → client-idempotent (same id+user → 200; soft-deleted or
cross-user → 409).

Dispatch a bot to join a Meet / Teams / Zoom meeting.

``BotDispatchRejected`` → 422 (bad URL / account);
``BotDispatchUnavailable`` → 503 (bot service offline).
